# Using SpecGate

When the user explicitly mentions SpecGate, load `specgate`. For
lifecycle work, load exactly one setup, preparation, or delivery phase before a
write. Read-only concept and troubleshooting questions stay in the root skill. Do
not apply the SpecGate lifecycle to generic specifications or work that is not
tied to SpecGate.
